window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>The world stands on the edge of catastrophe. Nether looms ready to swallow reality whole, while Disgardium spirals into chaos. Ancient powers stir from their slumber, threatening the delicate balance between worlds.<br> <br> Scyth returns from his exile in the beta-world more powerful than ever before, emerging as the last hope for salvation. He must battle through the final Demonic Games, unveil the secrets of ancient races and forgotten gods, and somehow unite former enemies against a common threat.<br> <br> Can Scyth, walking the knife's edge between worlds, halt the approaching apocalypse? What ultimate price must be paid to save the universe?<br> <br> This is the first volume of the final book in the seriesâ€”one that will answer these questions and forever change how you perceive the boundaries between reality and the virtual world.</p>"; 
